{"tid":2319879,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"穆迪對中國地方政府展望為負面","createTime":"2020-12-10T11:31:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-10T15:43:28.000Z","uid":75656,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"7da98c84c5892253cacacedf90eaf3116c59a86e","tid":2319879,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T11:31:20.000Z","msg":"評級機構穆迪發表報告指，中國在新型肺炎疫情中逐步復蘇，但各省的復蘇力度不同，經濟前景面臨的風險仍然傾向下行，對明年中國地方政府的展望為負面。<br />\n<br />\n報告指，地方政府的財政仍然受到稅基縮小，及對土地出讓收入較高依賴所挑戰，並更倚靠直接借款和中央轉移支付。地方政府的資金缺口不斷擴大，將加大依靠地方國企舉債，以支持公共基建投資的壓力，從而產生較高的或有負債風險。<br />\n<br />\n穆迪預計，中國今年經濟增長將大幅放緩至2.2%，明年則增長7%。但報告指，如果繼續減稅降費應對疫情衝擊，地方政府的一般公共預算收入的回升，將滯後於GDP反彈。<br />\n<br />\n穆迪又預計，今年地方政府的預算債務負擔，將達到財政收入約97%，而去年為83%。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1564463-20201209.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1564463-20201209.htm&d=DJHqE1tJ5F0S1%2BmpD1KYpmdKmUD4oZ9Yq66eb74BBG8%3D&h=937aa255\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1564463-20201209.htm&h=caa7b61b\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1564463-20201209.htm</a>"},{"pid":"8e566b58d43d3b48a0125158efbe7ae4c6c41ad1","tid":2319879,"uid":39733,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T11:33:03.000Z","msg":"評級機構幾時將中國同香港合體<br />\n將香港政府歸類為中國地方政府？"},{"pid":"858a3513871ec30c0c85f72093c642bcdf5c5536","tid":2319879,"uid":50502,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T11:33:13.000Z","msg":"穆迪違反國安法 即刻道歉"},{"pid":"bc5c306862c1aaebdffaa56ba5134fc19e68cf6d","tid":2319879,"uid":29153,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T11:35:53.000Z","msg":"国安法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d30252d821dfa84e1140e35bad30d54e2a8544fb","tid":2319879,"uid":45925,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7da98c84c5892253cacacedf90eaf3116c59a86e","tid":231987